If subject is present in SDTM.DM and not present in SDTM.AE then set to 'N', else if subject is present in SDTM.AE then set to 'Y'.
Extract date part from SDTM date variable and convert to CDASH date format (DD-MON-YYYY).
If SDTM.AE.AETERM is not null and SDTM.AE.AEENDTC is null then CDASH.AE.AEONGO='Y', else if SDTM.AE.AETERM is not null and SDTM.AE.AEENDTC is not null then CDASH.AE.AEONGO='N'.
Remove all records where SDTM.DS.DSDECOD="FINAL LAB VISIT" as these are derived records in SDTM.DS.
If SDTM.DS.DSDECOD='DEATH' then convert SDTM.DS.DSSTDTC to CDASH date format (DD-MON-YYYY).
If SDTM.CM.CMTERM is not null and SDTM.CM.CMENDTC is null then CDASH.CM.CMONGO='Y', else if SDTM.CM.CMTERM is not null and SDTM.CM.CMENDTC is not null then CDASH.CM.CMONGO='N'.
If SDTM.DS.DSTERM='PROTOCOL ENTRY CRITERIA NOT MET' and SDTM.DS.DSSEQ=SDTM.SUPPDS.DSSEQ then CDASH.IE.VISIT=SDTM.DS.VISIT.
If SDTM.DS.DSTERM='PROTOCOL ENTRY CRITERIA NOT MET' and SDTM.DS.DSSEQ=SDTM.SUPPDS.DSSEQ then CDASH.IE.VISDAT=SDTM.DS.DSDTC converted to CDASH date format (DD-MON-YYYY).
If subject is present in SDTM.DM and not present in SDTM.SUPPDS then set to 'No', else if subject is present in SDTM.SUPPDS then set to 'Yes'.
If CDASH.IE.IETESTCD begins with 'INCL' then set to 'INCLUSION', else if CDASH.IE.IETESTCD begins with 'EXCL' then set to 'EXCLUSION'.
CDASH.IE.IETESTCD=SDTM.TI.IETESTCD when SDTM.SUPPDS.QVAL value matches the last 2 characters of the SDTM.TI.IETESTCD value.
CDASH.IE.TEST=SDTM.TI.IETEST when SDTM.SUPPDS.QVAL value matches the last 2 characters of the SDTM.TI.IETESTCD value.
If CDASH.IE.IETESTCD begins with 'INCL' then set to 'No', else if CDASH.IE.IETESTCD begins with 'EXCL' then set to 'Yes'.
If SDTM.LB.VISIT=SDTM.SV.VISIT then extract the date part from SDTM.SV.SVSTDTC and convert to CDASH date format (DD-MON-YYYY).
Extract time part from SDTM date variable and convert to CDASH time format.
If SDTM.QS.QSTESTCD in ('ACTOT' 'NPTOT) <these are derived parameters created in SDTM.QS)> then CDASH.QS.QSORRES=SDTM.QS.QSSTRESC, else CDASH.QS.QSORRES=SDTM.QS.QSORRES.
If SDTM.SC.SCDTC=SDTM.SV.SVSTDTC and SDTM.SV.VISIT='SCREENING 1' then CDASH.SC.VISIT=SDTM.SV.VISIT.
If SDTM.SC.SCDTC=SDTM.SV.SVSTDTC and SDTM.SV.VISIT='SCREENING 1' then extract date part from SDTM.SV.SVSTDTC and convert to CDASH date format (DD-MON-YYYY).
If SDTM.VS.VSDTC=SDTM.SV.SVSTDTC then extract date part from SDTM.SV.SVSTDTC and convert to CDASH date format (DD-MON-YYYY).
CDASH.VS.DIABP_VSDAT=SDTM.VS.VSDTC when SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD='DIABP'. Date is converted to CDASH date format (DD-MON-YYYY).
CDASH.VS.HEIGHT_VSDAT=SDTM.VS.VSDTC when SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD='HEIGHT'. Date is converted to CDASH date format (DD-MON-YYYY).
CDASH.VS.PULSE_VSDAT=SDTM.VS.VSDTC when SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD='PULSE'. Date is converted to CDASH date format (DD-MON-YYYY).
CDASH.VS.SYSBP_VSDAT=SDTM.VS.VSDTC when SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD='SYSBP'. Date is converted to CDASH date format (DD-MON-YYYY).
CDASH.VS.TEMP_VSDAT=SDTM.VS.VSDTC when SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD='TEMP'. Date is converted to CDASH date format (DD-MON-YYYY).
CDASH.VS.WEIGHT_VSDAT=SDTM.VS.VSDTC when SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD='WEIGHT'. Date is converted to CDASH date format (DD-MON-YYYY).
